{
  "texts": [
    "Single Component Appearance: We consider cases where only a single component from the set appears in the input.",
    "There are n such samples, corresponding to each σ i ∈ Σ appearing alone.",
    "Missing Components: Samples are created for scenarios where any one of the components is missing, with the remaining n -1 components appearing in the correct sequence.",
    "where s -i = σ 1,..., σ i-1, σ i+1,..., σ n.",
    "There are n such samples, one for each component missing."
  ]
}